in every cycle where maingreen is high, either sidered or sideyellow should be high, and sidegreen should be low 
in every cycle where sidegreen is high, either mainred or mainyellow should be high, and maingreen should be low
only one among sidegreen, sidered and sideyellow should be high in any given cycle
only one among maingreen, mainred and mainyellow should be high in any given cycle
the mainroad should be serviced every once in a while, even if there are always cars waiting in side road to avoid congestion in mainroad